title: Episode Three: LADIES NIGHT! with Jazmyn Simon and Kirsten Nelson
description:
Happy Thanksgiving Psych-O's! Here's a special LADIES ONLY episode specifically about Psych 3: This is Gus. Sorry Tim! You were missed.

Juliet, Chief Vick, and Selene are back together again talking about their favorite memories from the movie, on set and off, maybe even a secret or two, and crying from laughter and laughing from crying.
